  "title": "Production & Operations Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Care for flowers and plants, maintain their optimum condition for storage and cleanliness</li>\n  <li>Getting the plants, flowers and supply ready for Florist. (E.g flower dethroning, base making, washing of flowers,etc)</li>\n  <li>Carefully arranging palatable bouquets and hampers to prevent damage during delivery</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Must haves!</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 day work week but able to work on weekends &amp; PH* on rotational shift (8am to 5.30pm &amp; 10.30am - 8pm &amp; 1230am-10pm) as we are a service industry</li>\n  <li>Job skills: Multitasking, responsive, team player</li>\n  <li>Preferably candidate to have a certification in Floristry and relevant working experience as Florist</li>\n  <li>Preferably at least 3 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Floral Assistant/Trainee Available for those with no experience</p>\n<p><em>*Will compensate accordingly for work done on PH</em></p>",
