    "description": "<p>For over 25 years, we help customers to celebrate their special moments by delivering fresh flowers and fabulous gifts. Ferns N Petals was established in 1994 and flower bouquet delivery was the first and only thing that the company was into. From just 1 flower shop in 1994, Ferns N Petals is now the largest florist chain with more than 320 stores worldwide. The brand is one stop shop for all gifting needs, be it buying flowers, cakes, plants, personalized gifts, decoration services, or experiences, across the globe.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join us?</strong></p>\n<p>We are expanding! &nbsp;You will be part of a team that will lead the growth of our company. There will be immense oportunity to learn and grow with us. If you are a driven, opportunistic and collaborative individual, come and join us!</p>",
